original_title: Van Morrison – Up on Cyprus Avenue
overview: An iconic artist of his generation, Van Morrison will celebrate his 70th birthday by appearing at this unique venue – a beautiful location made famous across the world through the song from his ground breaking and widely acclaimed Astral Weeks album, first released in 1968. This show played in August 2015 for the Eastside Arts Festival on Cyprus Avenue, the tree-lined Belfast street.
title: Van Morrison – Up on Cyprus Avenue
